Ann Murdock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ann_Murdock 0 Ann Murdock (November 10, 1890 – April 22, 1939) was a stage and silent film actress popular during the 1910s. She is sometimes billed as Anna Murdock. Ann_Murdock ( November_10_,_1890 – April_22_,_1939 ) was a_stage and silent_film_actress popular during the_1910s . She is_sometimes_billed as Anna_Murdock .
